alcharts.com/archive-chart/_/18/2011-02-19/|title=Chart Archive > 19 February 2011 > |publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]}}\n* For \"Give & Take\": {{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/18/2012-01-28/|title=Chart Archive > 28 January 2012 > |publisher=Official Charts Company}}\n* For \"Come Alive\": {{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/18/2012-06-02/|title=Chart Archive > 2 June 2012 > |publisher=Official Charts Company}}\n* For \"Love Has Gone\": {{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/18/2012-07-07/|title=Chart Archive > 7 July 2012 > |publisher=Official Charts Company}}\n* For \"Running Low\": {{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/18/2014-08-16/|title=Chart Archive > 16 August 2014 > |publisher=Official Charts Company}}\n* For \"Rio\": {{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/archive-chart/_/18/2015-10-15/|title=Chart Archive > 15 October 2015 > |publisher=Official Charts Company}}\n</ref>\n|-\n| 2010\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Moving with You]]\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Jenna Gibbons|Jenna G]])</span>\n| 64 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|''Netsky''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2012\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Give & Take]]\"\n| 17 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 196 || 30\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''2''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Come Alive (Netsky song)|Come Alive]]\"\n| 10 || 35 || \u2014 || 75 || \u2014 || 150 || 24\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Love Has Gone]]\"\n| 14 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 93 || 182 || 33\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[We Can Only Live Today (Puppy)]]\"{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"We Can Only Live Today (Puppy)\" appears on the deluxe edition of his second album ''[[2 (Netsky album)|2]]''.}}<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring Billie)</span>\n| 8 || \u2014 || 63 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n| 2014\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Running Low]]\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Beth Ditto]])</span>\n| 1 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 100 || \u2014 || 80 || 21\n| {{n/a|Non-album single}}\n|-\n| 2015\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Rio\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Digital Farm Animals]])</span>\n| 4 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 95 || 158 || 29\n| rowspan=\"2\"| ''3''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2016\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Work It Out\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring Digital Farm Animals)</span>\n| 5 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 188 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Rio\" (Remix)<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Macklemore]] and [[Digital Farm Animals]])</span>\n| \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"8\" {{n/a|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Who Knows\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Paije Richardson|Paije]])</span>\n| 30 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n| 2017\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Here with You]]\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Lost Frequencies]])</span>\n| 2 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 76 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2018\n! scope=\"row\"| \"T\u00e9quila Limonada\"<br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[A.Chal]])</span><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8469433/netsky-republic-casablanca-tequila-limonada-a-chal |title=Netsky Celebrates Republic/Casablanca Signing With 'Tequila Limonada': Exclusive |last=Bein |first=Kat |date=9 August 2018 |website=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180810001530/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8469433/netsky-republic-casablanca-tequila-limonada-a-chal |archive-date=10 August 2018 |accessdate=11 August 2018}}</ref>\n| 18 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ice Cold\"<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/10/premiere-netsky-david-guetta-ice-cold/ |title=Premiere: Netsky links with David Guetta for fiery 'Ice Cold' |last=Dexter |first=Robyn |date=11 October 2018 |website=[[Dancing Astronaut]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012063331/https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/10/premiere-netsky-david-guetta-ice-cold/ |archive-date=12 October 2018 |accessdate=12 October 2018}}</ref> <br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[David Guetta]])</span>\n| 71 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I Don't Even Know You Anymore\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2019/02/netsky-enlists-bazzi-lil-wayne-newest-release-dont-even-know-anymore/ |title=Netsky enlists Bazzi and Lil Wayne for newest release, 'I Don\u2019t Even Know You Anymore' |last=Sweeney |first=Farrell |date=19 February 2019 |website=Dancing Astronaut |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220054628/https://dancingastronaut.com/2019/02/netsky-enlists-bazzi-lil-wayne-newest-release-dont-even-know-anymore/ |archive-date=20 February 2019 |accessdate=20 February 2019}}</ref> <br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Bazzi (singer)|Bazzi]] and [[Lil Wayne]])</span>\n| 42 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Snitch\"<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2019/07/netsky-and-aloe-blaccs-snitch-captures-a-perfectly-complementary-collaborative-balance/ |title=Netsky and Aloe Blacc's 'Snitch' captures a perfectly complementary collaborative balance |last=Krinsky |first=Alexander |date=27 July 2019 |website=Dancing Astronaut |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190728040121/https://dancingastronaut.com/2019/07/netsky-and-aloe-blaccs-snitch-captures-a-perfectly-complementary-collaborative-balance/ |archive-date=28 July 2019 |accessdate=6 August 2019}}</ref> <br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[Aloe Blacc]])</span>\n| 58 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n| 2020\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I See the Future in Your Eyes\"