ikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|+ List of extended plays\n! scope=\"col\" | Title\n! scope=\"col\" | Details\n|-\n! scope=\"row\" | ''Abbot Kinney''<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/12/netsky-thrills-end-year-abbot-kinney-ep/ |title=Netsky thrills with end-of-year ''Abbot Kinney'' EP |last=Dexter |first=Robyn |date=15 December 2018 |website=[[Dancing Astronaut]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181219054151/https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/12/netsky-thrills-end-year-abbot-kinney-ep/ |archive-date=19 December 2018 |accessdate=19 December 2018}}</ref>\n\n| \n* Released: 14 December 2018\n* Label: BD Music Limited\n* Formats: [[Music download|Digital download]]\n|}\n\n===Singles===\n====As lead artist====\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"7\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Ultratop|BEL (FL)]]<br><ref name=belfl/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Austria|AUT]]<br><ref name=aut>{{cite web|url=http://www.austriancharts.at/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Netsky|title=Austrian Charts > Netsky|publisher=austriancharts.at/ Hung Medien}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[SNEP|FRA]]<br><ref name=fra>{{cite web|url=http://lescharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Netsky|title=French Charts > Netsky|publisher=lescharts.nl|accessdate=29 March 2013}}</ref> \n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Germany|GER]]<br><ref name=ger>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.de/artist.asp?name=Netsky&country=de|title=German Charts > Netsky|publisher=charts.de/ Hung Medien}}</ref>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:3em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Single Top 100|NL]]<br><ref name=nl>{{cite web|url=http://dutchcharts.nl/s