20180810001530/https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/8469433/netsky-republic-casablanca-tequila-limonada-a-chal |archive-date=10 August 2018 |accessdate=11 August 2018}}</ref>\n| 18 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Ice Cold\"<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/10/premiere-netsky-david-guetta-ice-cold/ |title=Premiere: Netsky links with David Guetta for fiery 'Ice Cold' |last=Dexter |first=Robyn |date=11 October 2018 |website=[[Dancing Astronaut]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181012063331/https://dancingastronaut.com/2018/10/premiere-netsky-david-guetta-ice-cold/ |archive-date=12 October 2018 |accessdate=12 October 2018}}</ref> <br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(with [[David Guetta]])</span>\n| 71 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n! scope=\"row\"| \"I Don't Even Know You Anymore\"<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2019/02/netsky-enlists-bazzi-lil-wayne-newest-release-dont-even-know-anymore/ |title=Netsky enlists Bazzi and Lil Wayne for newest release, 'I Don\u2019t Even Know You Anymore' |last=Sweeney |first=Farrell |date=19 February 2019 |website=Dancing Astronaut |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220054628/https://dancingastronaut.com/2019/02/netsky-enlists-bazzi-lil-wayne-newest-release-dont-even-know-anymore/ |archive-date=20 February 2019 |accessdate=20 February 2019}}</ref> <br><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Bazzi (singer)|Bazzi]] and [[Lil Wayne]])</span>\n| 42 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Snitch\"<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://dancingastronaut.com/2019/07/netsky-and-aloe-blaccs-snitch-captures-a-perfectly-complementary-collaborative-balance/ |title=Netsky and Aloe Blacc's 'Snitch' captures a perfectly complementary collaborative balance |last=Krinsky |first=Alexander |date=27 July 2019 |website=Dancing Astronaut |archive-url